                                    <strong>Wellness Exams: </strong>Annual or periodic wellness exams to assess overall health, discuss lifestyle habits, and identify potential health risks.
                                </p>
                                <p class="profile-position">
                                    <strong>Counseling and Education: </strong>Health education sessions on topics such as nutrition, exercise, smoking cessation, stress management, and other lifestyle modifications.
                                </p>
